milestones.description: Greenidge has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 479 runs, going past Clive Lloyd's 434
Asif Iqbal has broken the record for most ODIs (6) as captain for PAK, going past Wasim Bari
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (15) for WI, going past Deryck Murray
Sarfraz Nawaz has conceded the most runs in an innings (71) in ODIs for PAK, going past Asif Masood's record of 64
Majid Khan and Zaheer Abbas's 166-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 77 between Zaheer Abbas and Azmat Rana
This is the highest match aggregate (543) involving teams West Indies & Pakistan in ODIs
Majid Khan and Zaheer Abbas's 166-run partnership is PAK's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 159 between Sadiq Mohammad and Majid Khan
Majid Khan has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, breaking Ian Chappell's record
